# Turag, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Turag (; ) is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative centre of Turagsky Selsoviet, Tabasaransky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:  There are 8 streets.
Geography
Turag is located 17&nbsp;km south of Khuchni (the district's administrative centre) by road. Zirdag and Sika are the nearest rural localities.
